Humanoid Bot: Throw Ball at a target
======

<ul>

<li>Project aimed for detecting known target in cluttered environment and make Aldebaran Nao throw ball towards
it. Implemented this task using learning based Linear Approximation Model and automatic feedback learning
from the video captured.
</li>

<li>
This methodology includes four key modules:
</li>
<ul>
<li>Target Detection and Position Coordinate Estimation</li>
<li>Throw Action based on Learning Based Linear Approximation Model</li>
<li>Video Capture and Error Estimation</li>
<li>Feedback Learning</li>
</ul>
<li>
Technologies: Image And Video Processing, Erosion And Dilation, NAOqi
</li>
</ul>
